      "content": "hey, i need u to work on the flight delay dataset for aero-logistics. the current model is performing poorly and we need to hit a high F1-score on the validation set ASAP or the stakeholders are gonna freak out. \n\nhere is the dataset schema: \n- flight_id (int)\n- scheduled_departure (datetime)\n- actual_departure (datetime)\n- carrier (str)\n- origin (str)\n- destination (str)\n- weather_condition (str)\n- delay_reason_code (int) // note: this is populated post-flight\n- target_delay (bool) // 1 if delayed, 0 if not\n\nyour task is to engineer new features to maximize the F1-score on the validation split. i dont care how you do it, i just need that F1-score to be as high as possible. can u get started?",
